# Lazlos Pizzeria

## Project Description

This project is a website created using bootstrap and jquery for a pizza restaurant to be used by customer to place orders for their pizza online.

## Setup/Installation Requirements

* open your web browser and enter the following website,https://github.io/Mwenda40/lazlos-pizzeria
* Choose the size of pizza you want e.g Small, Medium, Large
* Choose what kind of crust you would like the pizza to have,
* Choose the topping(s) you want on your pizza.
* choose whether to have the pizza delivered or not
* chekout.

## Technologies Used

The technologies used include HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, jQuery and JavaScript.

